        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Zend_Filter offers $filter->setEncoding('utf-8'), but when used with Zend_Form developer can't set that anywhere cetrally. There should be a static call to set encoding to UTF-8 for all filters application-wide. \n\nCurrent workaround is to create Filters separetly and set encoding for each of them. "
